{
  "stem": "3973.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she-- she was a Kempler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was living with some-- you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was told and recommend, give her away for adoption to you sister, which I did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So this sister-- this-- the-- I developed, among my mental quirks-- not only the running away as I did from my parents.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I began to run away from people before I got too close to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because every time, love and death to me became synonymous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Whenever I loved somebody, they died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So it became bad words.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My vocabulary love is bad word, mother a bad word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They all produced reaction, which I didn't know how to cope with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is-- was my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then after she died, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I switch companies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to work for a company in Connecticut, the magnetic tape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to commute from New York to Connecticut for a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the job was ideal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's all kinds of opportunity, all kinds of growth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- I did very well, as usual, by-- this was sufficiently new field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was-- there was-- no-- there's no place-- you can't learn about in school, anyplace else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was always ahead of everybody else, because I had the books nobody else wanted to read.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Intellectually, I was functioning very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So from all outward appearancing, I was as normal as can be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Emotionally, I was totally stuck and frozen in place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Frozen would be a good way to describe it, or paralyzed, or even dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just knew something was wrong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I knew I would not-- I would gradually over the time give up friends, not pursue writing letters or keeping in touch, or making friends.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
